item.title: 455 Days
item.description: 455 days ago today I started work at a fairly large medical software company in Madison, Wisconsin. About 3 weeks in I realized I didn’t want to be there1 very long. Anyway its 1am now, maybe day 456 will be better. There? Here? Hard to say which is right but I’m still here as of today. !
